query:
SELECT
                           r.id as "rid: ReleaseId",
                           c.name as "name: KrateName",
                           r.version as "version: Version"
                       FROM
                            crates as c
                            INNER JOIN releases as r ON c.id = r.crate_id
                       WHERE
                            r.archive_storage = FALSE
                       ORDER BY r.id
                       LIMIT $1
